ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 145 - (Sakatchewan) Provincial Emergencies Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER N° 145 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of SASKATCHEWAN with respect to the RAINSTORM that affected the region south of Montreal Lake from June 16 to 18, 2010.
